ol.li: CPU pushes: SS, ESP, EFLAGS, CS, EIP (SS/ESP only on privilege change)
pusha pushes: EDI, ESI, EBP, ESP, EBX, EDX, ECX, EAX
Stub pushes: GS, FS, ES, DS

ul.li: cs at offset 0x3C Code segment selector
eflags at offset 0x40 CPU flags (IF, etc.)
useresp at offset 0x44 User stack (if ring change)
ss at offset 0x48 User stack segment (if ring change) iret Restoration Order: eip cs eflags [useresp ss]
